'''霹雳贝贝'''（Wonder boy）是中国1988年拍摄的电影，<ref name="#1">{{Cite news|url=http://www.1905.com/mdb/film/63773/filmtag/|title=霹雳贝贝标签|language=zh-cn|publisher=_电影网|author=|date=|accessdate=2016-03-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160409121603/http://www.1905.com/mdb/film/63773/filmtag/|archivedate=2016-04-09}}</ref>讲述的是主人公贝贝，因为在母亲生自己时，一个不明飞行物一闪而过，让自己有能操控电和电器的能力。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://mt.sohu.com/20150620/n415368340.shtml|title=霹雳贝贝|language=zh-cn|publisher=搜狐|author=|date=|accessdate=2016-03-26|archive-date=2016-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160406073340/http://mt.sohu.com/20150620/n415368340.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

